_sText:
You have 3 hp and you have to hit/kill the enemy
with a smoke, flash or that he fall down the pit.

The map is very foggy, additional with right thrown
smokes and flashes, its very hard to see where
your going to, so be carefull what your doing.

In the back, right corner is a secret ladder.
Downstairs you can find a knife and move to the
enemys secret ladder.

-----------------------------------------------
-----------------------------------------------

Because the category "Dodgeball" does not
exist, I put this map on "Grenade War".

[-Its not the Final, so plz do not rate too hard.]
